  "title": "Tapping to welcome windfalls",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute tapping script for releasing the belief that big financial surprises are for other people.",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 33 of the MONEY program. The script targets the habit of discounting unexpected income before it arrives: the voice that says it can't last, there's a catch, or big luck isn't available to you.",
