        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 33 of the MONEY program. The session works with the reflex that downgrades big financial surprises: the waiting for the reversal, the checking for the catch, the quiet belief that large unexpected money is for other people.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
